<BlogPost
  title="CLAUDE.md vs .cursorrules vs AGENTS.md: how to configure any AI coding tool"
  description="Every AI coding tool has its own config format. Here's what each one does, how they differ, and how to manage all four without duplicating your conventions across every repo."
